# Fluxbox keybindings – Mac-inspired
Mod1 Tab :NextWindow {groups} (workspace=[current])
Mod1 Shift Tab :PrevWindow {groups} (workspace=[current])
Mod1 F4 :Close
Mod1 F9 :Minimize
Control Mod1 t :Exec xterm -T "Terminal" -e "cd /workspace && bash"
Control Mod1 Delete :Exec xterm -T "System Info" -hold -e "top"
